{"tid":2139993,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"「世紀公投」阿仙奴是否有資格入Big 6","createTime":"2020-08-04T15:59:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T06:32:10.000Z","uid":320688,"like":86,"dislike":216,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"c97047cb0a2d7255e180b36fdadfb63319a1d8f2","tid":2139993,"uid":320688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T15:59:39.000Z","msg":"現在英超Big 6 包括 曼聯、阿仙奴、車路士、利物浦、曼城、熱刺。<br />\n近年有不少非big 6球隊成績優異（李斯特城，狼隊等）李斯特城更在15/16球季取得英超冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n阿仙奴上次奪冠已經係16年前，隨着雲加退休，連續四年冇歐聯打，實力早已令人懷疑，甚至今季跌至聯賽第8位，再加上多次買入車路士舊將（施治，大衛雷斯，韋利安）被連登網民取笑為（車仔垃圾收容所）。即使足總杯以2-1擊敗車路士取得冠軍，但比賽過程中存在唔少受爭議嘅判決。雖然如此，阿仙奴球迷仍然覺得阿仙奴係北倫敦之王，由此可見，阿仙奴球迷質素低劣。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KSGWOV5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKSGWOV5.jpg&h=59d58c6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有，03/04 全季不敗已經夠做<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇，李斯特城值得擁有Big 6"},{"pid":"5b72fdfc4e6abfe406e4aed19e3613f8b2bf511d","tid":2139993,"uid":13395,"like":60,"dislike":1,"score":59,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T16:01:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />熱狗英超都未撚拎過"},{"pid":"289b51fe1843455cd751387a59af0ce2e99727a4","tid":2139993,"uid":7922,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T16:02:33.000Z","msg":"熱狗個獎盃櫃吉架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13452dbf5f06e9db39f9a4c03138c42a0b6282ce","tid":2139993,"uid":148002,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T16:04:00.000Z","msg":"個post 係唔係熱狗開<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5709f26944085988a5d8a9ca461416ae2ac7ceda","tid":2139993,"uid":148002,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2